    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total stunner! This car has been pampered since day one\u2014always garaged, hand-washed, and treated like royalty. It honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! You won't find a single blemish or speck of dust anywhere; it\u2019s just that perfect. If you're looking for that brand-new feel and a smooth, flawless drive, this is the one for you. Come say hi and take a look\u2014you definitely won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black Metallic. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that has been professionally overhauled. The power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via a factory Variable M Differential Lock. Crucially, the rear subframe has been structurally reinforced, and the rod bearings have been replaced as a proactive measure, ensuring the mechanical integrity of the powertrain. The chassis retains its original suspension geometry with no bushing play, and the 19-inch Style 67 forged wheels are wrapped in fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber. The interior remains in showroom state, featuring Cinnamon Nappa leather with no bolster wear and a pixel-perfect instrument cluster. This is a definitive enthusiast's example, free of any aerodynamic or mechanical modifications.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
