      "price": 44000.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true automotive masterpiece in absolute showroom condition. This vehicle appears as if it just rolled off the assembly line, featuring a deep, mirror-like exterior finish with zero imperfections, having been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the cabin retains its original new-car scent, with supple leather seating showing no signs of wear and a dashboard untouched by the sun. Every electronic component and tactile switch functions with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is flawless, supported by a complete, documented service history and exceptionally low mileage. This is a rare opportunity to own a specimen that looks, feels, and drives exactly like it did on day one. Includes all original manuals, keys, and accessories.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
